# =============================================================================
# CIA Directorate of Support — Discord webhook configuration
# =============================================================================
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Paste each channel webhook URL (https://discord.com/api/webhooks/...)
# 3. Never commit .env
#
# Full catalog: see README.md → Announcer catalog
# =============================================================================

